<view class="container safe"><view class="title">包裹 NFC 确认取件</view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">读取包裹 NFC 标签</view><view class="subtitle">靠近包裹标签；NFC 不可用时可手动输入 payload，仍会请求真实 server。</view><button class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="read">读取 NFC 标签</button><textarea class="input" placeholder="sps://pickup?... 或 JSON" bindinput="input" value="{{raw}}"></textarea><view class="notice">{{tagText}}</view></view><button class="btn btn-primary" loading="{{submitting}}" bindtap="confirmServer">确认已取件</button><view class="success" wx:if="{{resultText}}">{{resultText}}</view></view>
